WEBVTT

1
00:15:22.050 --> 00:15:24.850 
不知道  我妻子可不喜欢单数
I don't know. My wife hated odd numbers.

2
00:15:27.190 --> 00:15:28.560 
你好
Well, hello, there.

3
00:15:28.660 --> 00:15:31.100 
达克·菲利普斯  你认识莫娜吧
Duck Phillips, you know Mona.

4
00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:32.160 
当然
Of course.

5
00:15:32.270 --> 00:15:33.760 
你好
Hello.

6
00:15:33.870 --> 00:15:36.560 
然后这位是佩特拉  克莱伯·卡尔森
Of course this is Petra and Crab Colson.

7
00:15:37.770 --> 00:15:40.930 
克莱伯  达克  达克  克莱伯
Crab, Duck. Duck, Crab.

8
00:15:41.040 --> 00:15:42.740 
你要喝点什么
Can I get you something?

9
00:15:42.840 --> 00:15:44.170 
番茄汁吧  如果有的话
Tomato juice, if you have it.

10
00:15:44.280 --> 00:15:45.610 
拜托
Come on.

11
00:15:45.710 --> 00:15:47.510 
