I'll have something with dinner.

12
00:15:47.610 --> 00:15:49.310 
沿途风景很美
Beautiful drive.

13
00:15:49.420 --> 00:15:50.680 
-你走锯木厂那条路了  -是的
- Did you take the Sawmill? - I did.

14
00:15:50.780 --> 00:15:53.080 
